title: Click Click Boom
lastfmSummary: "Click Click Boom" is a song by American rock band Saliva. It was released in 2001 on their second album Every Six Seconds as the lead single. The song was later re-recorded, entitled "Click Click Pull", in response to the September 11, 2001 attacks. * Official theme song for WWF No Mercy 2001. * Used in the films; The Fast and the Furious (although it was not on the main OST, however the song's music video can be found on the Special Edition DVD release) Read more on Last.fm.
